    <note>Wei(2) Yilin [10046] Author of the Shi yi de xiao fang, 20 ch., which is a collection of his family medical formula for five generations. He held office as medical instructor of his native county, Nanfeng. He completed the work in 1337 and wrote the earliest preface in 1345. Ding Fubao, 502a-502b; SKTY, 104.3b. He is most probably related to the Song Jianchang Wei(2) [zu #521]. WDY, 1, 290.</note>
